Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個被稱為NAC的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前幾天的圍剿中 雖然想抓住NAC的把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可惜資料都已被埋在沙土之下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而其嫌疑重大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是先把他們鎮壓了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 名門和財閥的集合體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是歷史的遺物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這終究只不過是謠傳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有真憑實據
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把他們鎮壓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELEVEN的經濟就會止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對本國的稅收也會造成影響
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且讓NUMBERS管理NUMBERS是帝國的大原則
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼黑之騎士團的搜索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從殘留下的挖掘機械(Shield Machine)來看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以判明成田的事是ZERO所為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但除了團員屍骸以外 找不到更多的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能對京都出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又無法把ZERO逼入絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從結果上來看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的無能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到布里塔尼亞的皇女竟如此厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放戰線分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的希望之火已經熄滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未可斷言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說還在逃亡中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但籐堂還健在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說連無賴·改也失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之騎士團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮二式也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從樞木朱雀救出事件以來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您對ZERO很執著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於特拉法爾加(Trafalgar)戰役的敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[1805年,在納爾遜指揮下的英國艦隊於直布羅陀海峽西北的\N特拉法爾加角擊敗法國和西班牙聯合艦隊的海戰。挫敗了拿破侖\N登陸英國本土的作戰計劃。英國掌握了制海權，納爾遜戰死。]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊麗莎白三世被革命勢力圍困在愛丁堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}當時布里塔尼亞軍鎮守在殖民地美洲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}也就是我們現在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 心事重重的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便秘? 宿醉?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是因為魯魯修不在而感到寂寞?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是… 卡蓮也和他一起缺席了 又一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真悠閒啊 全世界都在討論前天的成田事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀今天仍然因此請假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對我來說 魯魯和卡蓮的事更成問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛啊 莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是喜歡你這種性格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別拿我尋開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說嘛 你直說不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『我喜歡你』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這可不行啊! 不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒絕了該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定連普通朋友也做不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也用不著… 笑得那麼誇張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很開心呢 現在這個地方 現在的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是稍微有點覺悟的好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不變的事物在哪兒都是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不要變得那麼嚴肅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果無論如何都想知道的話 乾脆去問本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是怎麼想的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯…魯魯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天不是休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉稍微有點發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲世子白天有點事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小娜娜的情況好點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長 那個文件…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分發到各年級的各個班上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這麼會使喚人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個能幹的部下真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部下?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 也還真是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對心臟不好啊 那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧? 門票…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些文件裡有沒有混雜我的信?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡思亂想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一起去聽音樂會而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這是個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都稱讚我們很好地使用了紅蓮二式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 卻被那個白色機甲…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平手啦 平手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉她怎麼了 突然間…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸單身赴任去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不想讓我寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以經常會給我送來這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說這傢伙不懂什麼叫開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉城你笑得太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都來的詔書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說非常希望與我們直接會面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是需要如此大驚小怪的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此大驚小怪? 那可是京都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果得到他們承認的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會獲得資金援助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們拮据的財政也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,財政?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果按我計劃的預算來辦的話 應該沒問題才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經是大組織了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人員增加的事可是預料之外的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝成大人物帶著新人縱情奢侈也是預料之外?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 今後會計的工作就改由扇負責
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來錢都是交給我來管的 現在卻要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若想讓人信任的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拿出相應的成果來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼資格說我?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自稱是同伴 卻連臉都不給我們看的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣啊 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 你這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的真面目是什麼無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO有著比那個柯內莉婭更勝一籌的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們黑之騎士團的首領啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要其他什麼來證明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妮娜…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果身體不舒服的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 我們本來是直人的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果身為妹妹的卡蓮都不介意的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為作為首領二代的你把位子讓給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成田的時候大家也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那時幾乎是脅迫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然對我們這些幹部也保密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已將可能的範圍縮小到12人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就是抽中哪根簽的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是需要隨機應變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說了些冒失的話 實在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮 你也想知道我的真面目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人 可是知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒好像已經退了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許只是身體任性了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近心裡一直有種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥好像要去很遠的地方似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可能是身體希望得到照顧 自然地配合了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠都會在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我再任性一下可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再握著我的手一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是這樣獨自睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得又會做那個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事想要拜託我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會按照你給我的提示行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論京都那邊的意圖是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都想要得到那些人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且對你的生存來說是必要的話 我也可以幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C. 我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 這是你忘了的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是今天什麼時候能回來都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備打電話拒絕她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約就應該要遵守啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 魯魯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於今天的約會 我可能會遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 肯定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 肯定會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[東京租界中央單軌鐵路線  至成田]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把其他的幹部也帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人是這麼吩咐的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓他們在周圍警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去叫他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在此之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破損較嚴重的屍體送到第二帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有遺物的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡快確認其身份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已確認身份的送到第一帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並以登記發現的場所與時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二醫療班馬上就要到達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場作業人員立刻趕往臨設帳篷…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在嗎  她… 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,官方資料裡她已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經滿足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體發掘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 希望能讓我繼續救援作業
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在你死心之前 請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼說也算是柯內莉婭殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO…黑之騎士團到底想要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們以這種犧牲為代價
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想要成就何種偉業?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正義的使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照他本人的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是正義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會想要討論『什麼是正義』這種讓人害臊的理論吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好歹也算是軍人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Energy Filler的更換
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我調查過了 純血派的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  是輻射波動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然協助敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個拉庫夏塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的機師也是S級的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在朱雀精神仍不穩定的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再次和這種對手戰鬥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想說贏不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微冷靜一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上升
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給各位帶來諸多不便了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人已恭候多時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡… 是富士礦山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能來得到這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不會有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座山 這個形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說 這個下面就有Sakuradite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誘發戰爭的罪魁禍首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 若發現入侵者 可是格殺勿論的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然把勢力滲透到這種地方來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都果然厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很醜惡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去曾經如此山清水秀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以流水清澈 綠秀富饒而著稱的靈峰富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也向帝國低頭屈服 任憑其不斷凌辱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全就是雖仍生存卻被不斷凌辱的我們日本的寫照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等可悲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不以真面目面對你們 我為此無禮而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是ZERO 這點你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須得看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看吧 你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO賜予了我們力量與勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫扇的是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把ZERO的假面拿下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也想相信… 你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 請讓我相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女…女人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人不是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見過她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾見過她和ZERO在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你  不是日本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES 京都的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐原泰三
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能讓知道大人真面目的人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不用說她還不是日本人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和我無關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是軟弱啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且行事手段和思想都太過迂腐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你們才贏不了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被遙控射擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 誰也不許動手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐原泰三
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuradite採掘業務參與者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐原產業的創始人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木政權的幕後中心人物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 戰敗後搖身一變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為支持殖民地統治的積極協力者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人稱 『賣國賊桐原』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 其真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻是管理全國抵抗組織的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都六家的要人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽奉陰違
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真穩妥的手段呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 不得對大人無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠如您所猜測
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  不是日本人!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得不能讓我們看到臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然並非生為日本人 為何要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:18:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞的毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能實現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有著必須那樣做的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對象是你實在是太幸運了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐原公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是八年前被送來作為人質的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時承蒙您多方照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果交涉對象是其他人的話 你會把他當作人質吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的 僅僅是提出願望而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八年前的種子開花了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此人毫無疑問是布里塔尼亞的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其不願顯露面容的理由我也瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以保證
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟隨ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據點隱蔽以及情報搜尋這些我們也會協助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 桐原公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要踏上 修羅之路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 這是我的命運的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2  第5  第7  第8  第9小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續在管理總部進行確認作業
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尼特的拼法是這樣的話 確實是這位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 由於現在情況特殊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 不會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請您確認
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然已經不在了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之一切從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:21:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之騎士團真正成為如我所願而行動的組織了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 對不起我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你已經走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 先不管那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之先找個避雨的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是弱者的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為什麼要殺了我爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他 很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來都沒有打過我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼壞事都沒有做過…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 卻被活埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦地窒息而死…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼爸爸要拋下我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.33,0:23:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又為何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.22,0:23:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從舞台上消失是很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:23:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要捨棄ZERO這一存在就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要封住桐原的口
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能變回魯魯修·蘭佩魯基
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 可是…
